# Django RLS

[![PyPI version](https://badge.fury.io/py/django-rls.svg)](https://badge.fury.io/py/django-rls)
[![PyPI - Downloads](https://img.shields.io/pypi/dm/django-rls)](https://pypi.org/project/django-rls/)
